The '''Khoisan Aboriginal and Others Movement ''' is a [[political party]] in [[South Africa]]. It is the first [[Khoisan]] party in South Africa and was launched in December 2008. It is led by [[Rodney January]] and will seek to improve the livelihood of South Africa's [[San people]].<ref>[http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/Politics/0,,2-7-12_2444493,00.html SA's first San party launches] news24.com, 20 December 2008 ([https://web.archive.org/web/20090204073752/http://www.news24.com/News24/South_Africa/Politics/0,,2-7-12_2444493,00.html archive link])</ref>

